title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Living organ donors outpace dead donors [headline from the The Journal News (Westchester County, New York) April 23, 2002. Submitted by Stephen E. Hirschberg, MD. Elmsford, NY, who writes “This is consistent with the medical aphorism “Death is God's way of telling you to slow down.”]
